            <description><![CDATA[<pre>Fixes
- Ignores benign cancelled network requests (`NSURLErrorCancelled`, code `-999`) in Sentry error capture.
- Uploads Recappi Mini debug symbols to Sentry during release builds so future macOS stack traces can be symbolicated.

Diagnostics
- Keeps real network failures such as timeouts, offline errors, and server errors reportable while reducing noisy Sentry alerts during Cloud refresh/navigation.</pre>]]></description>
